example_input_question: Which instance has the most memory?
example_output_query: SELECT instance_name, instance_memory, instance_memory_unit FROM ec2_pricing ORDER BY instance_memory DESC LIMIT 5;

example_input_question: Which instance has the most cpus?
example_output_query: SELECT instance_name, number_vcpus FROM ec2_pricing  ORDER BY number_vcpus DESC LIMIT 5;
